        <lb L="start">Booker T.</lb>
        <lb L="1">Was a practical <rhyme verb="1">man.</rhyme></lb>
        <lb L="2">He said, Till the soil</lb>
        <lb L="3">And learn from the <rhyme verb="1">land.</rhyme></lb>
        <lb L="4">Let down your bucket</lb>
        <lb L="5"> Where you <rhyme verb="2">are.</rhyme></lb>
